          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The brand is named after the German word for ‘close’, as the entire range consists of tools to keep your essential items near. A colorful series of pouches, pencases and holders for documents or iPad’s alike, providing you with various options of colors and purposes.</p>"
          }
        },
        "p_2": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Nähe is a Hightide brand, and their attention to design can be seen throughout the entire Hightide range of casual everyday stationery.</p>"
